INFO  2023-05-05 15:53:24,552 [42   ] oft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command - Executed DbCommand (304ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__Now_0='?' (DbType = DateTime2)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [a].[Id], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[CreatorUserId], [a].[IsAbandoned], [a].[JobArgs], [a].[JobType], [a].[LastTryTime], [a].[NextTryTime], [a].[Priority], [a].[TryCount]
FROM [AbpBackgroundJobs] AS [a]
WHERE [a].[IsAbandoned] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [a].[NextTryTime] <= @__Now_0
ORDER BY [a].[Priority] DESC, [a].[TryCount], [a].[NextTryTime]

INFO  2023-05-05 15:53:31,957 [41   ] oft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command - Executed DbCommand (262ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__Now_0='?' (DbType = DateTime2)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [a].[Id], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[CreatorUserId], [a].[IsAbandoned], [a].[JobArgs], [a].[JobType], [a].[LastTryTime], [a].[NextTryTime], [a].[Priority], [a].[TryCount]
FROM [AbpBackgroundJobs] AS [a]
WHERE [a].[IsAbandoned] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [a].[NextTryTime] <= @__Now_0
ORDER BY [a].[Priority] DESC, [a].[TryCount], [a].[NextTryTime]
